quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  11,61,WE ‘ILA THEMUDE ‘EHAHUM SALIHÆN KALE JA KAWMI A’BUDU ELLAHE MA LEKUM MIN ‘ILEHIN GAJRUHU HUWE ‘ENSHE’EKUM MINEL-’ERDI WE ESTA’MEREKUM FIHA FASTEGFIRUHU THUMME TUBU ‘ILEJHI ‘INNE RABBI KARIBUN MUXHIBUN
  11,62,KALU JA SALIHU KAD KUNTE FINA MERXHUWÆN KABLE HADHA ‘ETENHANA ‘EN NA’BUDE MA JA’BUDU ‘ABA’UUNA WE ‘INNENA LEFI SHEKKIN MIMMA TED’UNA ‘ILEJHI MURIBIN
  11,63,KALE JA KAWMI ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN KUNTU ‘ALA BEJJINETIN MIN RABBI WE ‘ATANI MINHU REHMETEN FEMEN JENSURUNI MINEL-LAHI ‘IN ‘ASEJTUHU FEMA TEZIDUNENI GAJRE TEHSIRIN
  11,64,WE JA KAWMI HEDHIHI NAKATU ELLAHI LEKUM ‘AJETEN FEDHERUHA TE’KUL FI ‘ERDI ELLAHI WE LA TEMESSUHA BISU’IN FEJE’HUDHEKUM ‘ADHABUN KARIBUN
  11,65,FE’AKARUHA FEKALE TEMETTA’U FI DARIKUM THELATHETE ‘EJJAMIN DHALIKE WA’DUN GAJRU MEKDHUBIN
  11,66,FELEMMA XHA’E ‘EMRUNA NEXHXHEJNA SALIHÆN WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ME’AHU BIREHMETIN MINNA WE MIN HIZJI JEWMI’IDHIN ‘INNE REBBEKE HUWEL-KAWIJUL-’AZIZU
  11,67,WE ‘EHADHEL-LEDHINE DHELEMU ES-SEJHETU FE’ESBEHU FI DIJARIHIM XHATHIMINE
  11,68,KE’EN LEM JEGNEW FIHA ‘ELA ‘INNE THEMUDE KEFERU REBBEHUM ‘ELA BU’DÆN LITHEMUDE